```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('o', 'oa')

print(insert_after_character('hello world'))  # prints "helloa world"
print(insert_after_character('foobar'))  # prints "foaoobar"
print(insert_after_character('loop'))  # prints "looaop"
print(insert_after_character('goodbye'))  # prints "goaodbye"
```
